/*create a project, package.
Create a class MyArea, in it declare the constant PI = 3.14 and the static method areaOfCircle, which
should take the radius and use PI to calculate the area of the circle.
Create a Main class where to run this method.*/

package packageOne;

public class MyArea {
    final static double PI = 3.14;

    static double areaOfCircle (int radius){
        double area = PI*Math.pow(radius,2);
        return area;
    }
}

package packageOne;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
    System.out.println(MyArea.areaOfCircle(2));
    }
}
